---
// Jamie's page, in his own words. Drafted with him 18 July 2026; edit only
// at his request.
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Why this exists"
  description="The story behind Executor File, told plainly by its maker."
>
  <div class="wrap prose">
    <section class="section">
      <h1>Why this exists</h1>

      <p>
        My dad died, and I was his executor. What I had to work with was the
        letters I found in his house. That was it. No list, no register,
        nothing that said what he had or where it was. I worked through it the
        only way you can, one letter and one statement at a time. I think I
        did everything. But I had no way of knowing where to start, and I
        still have no way of knowing what I missed. That is the part that
        stays: not the work, the not-knowing.
      </p>
      <p>
        Grief is heavy enough on its own. Adding months of searching for
        assets on top of it is a weight nobody should hand the people they
        love. I do not want to leave that to my kids. When I die I want it to
        be easy for them, and I want what I have to reach the people I love,
        not sit lost in accounts nobody knows exist.
      </p>
      <p>
        What I needed then did not exist in a form I trusted to still be there
        when it mattered: a plain record of what exists, where it is, and what
        you want done about it, kept by the family rather than by a company.
        So I built it. It is an encrypted file and one printed page.
        Everything else about it follows from that experience.
      </p>

      <p class="signature">
        Jamie Watters ·{' '}
        <a href="https://jamiewatters.work">jamiewatters.work</a>
      </p>

      <div class="doors">
        <p>
          <strong>Putting your affairs in order?</strong>{' '}
          <a href="/get-started">Get started</a>
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Someone has died and you have the printed page?</strong>{' '}
          <a href="/recover">Open the Executor File</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Base>

